title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Beechcraft Bonanza G36 - autopilot
description:
In this how to we are going to look how we to use the autopilot in a Beechcraft Bonanza G36.

We will depart from Rotterdam The Hague Airport
(EHRD) Runway 24 and make a small flight where we will use the autopilot functionalities. After this we land again on runway 24 using the approach function of the autopilot
